    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is accepted at Medium assurance level. All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the study protocol operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five flow-speed combinations.",
